item.title: CLI Tool - goris
item.description: Overview This is a CLI tool to search for images with Google Reverse Image Search. Motivation Because I had wanted to search for images with an image URL and file on my terminal, I created this. This can download images from searched image URLs. The detail information and how to get this are https://github.com/tanaikech/goris.
